<p><img src="http://butlerjcr.co.uk/application/views/involved/img/upload/085.jpg" alt="" />Butler Male Voices Choir</p><p><br />Key values of the choir:<br />- Be as open as possible, try not to focus to<span class="text_exposed_show">o much on quality but be more about some guys getting together and singing some decent music.<br />- Have regular, well attended socials.<br />- Be as democratic as possible, songs are voted on and chosen by all members.<br />- No auditions.<br />- Be committed, if you can&rsquo;t make a rehearsal apologise to the group in advance of the meeting to explain why you can&rsquo;t make it.<br />- Social members welcome.</span></p><p><span class="text_exposed_show"><img src="http://butlerjcr.co.uk/application/views/involved/img/upload/094.jpg" alt="" /></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Best new society 2015!</p><p><img src="http://butlerjcr.co.uk/application/views/involved/img/upload/090.jpg" alt="" /></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span class="text_exposed_show">This year the society cycled the Coast2Coast and raised over &pound;1500 for charity.</span></p><p><span class="text_exposed_show"><img src="http://butlerjcr.co.uk/application/views/involved/img/upload/089.jpg" alt="" /></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span class="text_exposed_show">A link to our facebook page is below:</span></p><p><span class="text_exposed_show"><a href="https://www.facebook.com/groups/742061735868535/">https://www.facebook.com/groups/742061735868535/</a></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span class="text_exposed_show">If you have any questions please contact James or Alex at:</span></p><p><span class="text_exposed_show"><a href="mailto:a.j.naylor@durhamac.uk">a.j.naylor@durhamac.uk</a>&nbsp;or&nbsp;<a href="https://www.facebook.com/AlexNaylor314">https://www.facebook.com/AlexNaylor314</a></span></p><p><span class="text_exposed_show"><a href="mailto:j.a.bowmer@durham.ac.uk">j.a.bowmer@durham.ac.uk</a>&nbsp;or&nbsp;<a href="https://www.facebook.com/JamesBowmer18?fref=ts">https://www.facebook.com/JamesBowmer18?fref=ts</a></span></p>